# Diya Pharma — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete, production-ready pharmaceutical e-commerce website for **Diya Pharma** supporting both retail and wholesale operations. The design is inspired by [vibcare.co.in](https://vibcare.co.in) with a premium green/white pharmaceutical aesthetic.

