## Design System

| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Primary** | `#0A6E3D` (forest green) → `#0D8C4D` → `#2ECC71` |
| **Accent** | `#E8A317` (gold) for special CTAs |
| **Font Headings** | Poppins (600-800 weight) |
| **Font Body** | Inter (400-600 weight) |
| **Border Radius** | 8px buttons, 12px cards, 16px modals |
| **Shadows** | 3-tier: `sm`, `md`, `lg` + green glow for primary buttons |
| **Transitions** | 150ms (fast), 300ms (base), 500ms (slow) |

### Button Specifications (matching vibcare.co.in)

| Button | Padding | Font | Colors | Hover |
|--------|---------|------|--------|-------|
| **Primary** | 12px 32px | Poppins 600, 14px, uppercase | Green gradient bg, white text | Darker green, translateY(-2px), stronger shadow |
| **Secondary** | 12px 32px | Poppins 600, 14px, uppercase | Transparent bg, green border+text | Green fill, white text |
| **Accent** | 12px 32px | Poppins 600, 14px, uppercase | Gold gradient bg, white text | Darker gold, translateY(-2px) |

