## Key Technical Features

- **localStorage persistence** — Cart, user sessions, and orders persist across browser refreshes
- **52 pharmaceutical products** with real-world compositions and pricing (MRP/PTR/PTS)
- **Multi-criteria filtering** — Combine division, form, therapeutic, price range
- **Responsive** — 4 breakpoints (480, 768, 1024, 1280px) with hamburger menu
- **Scroll animations** — IntersectionObserver-based fade-in effects
- **Toast notifications** — Slide-in confirmations for cart/form actions
- **Carousel system** — Reusable class with autoplay, responsive perView

