## How to Run

1. Open `c:\Users\DELL\Desktop\Diya Pharma\index.html` in any modern browser
2. No build step, no server, no dependencies required
3. All pages are linked — click through the full user flow

> [!TIP]
> For the best experience, use a local server to avoid CORS issues:
> ```
> cd "c:\Users\DELL\Desktop\Diya Pharma"
> npx -y serve .
> ```

